This page provides more information about the program and a direct contact with its @{"author" link "Author" 0}. All information contained in this page can be freely distribuited if not altered and the source always mentioned. In case of doubt about usage or possible bugs, don't esitate to contact the author.

Internet Providers who use @{b}HTTPJ@{ub} to maintain a Mirror on their site can be part of a particular support program:  for more informations read the WWW page above.

