@Node "Future" "HTTPJ v2.00 - Future of program"

   My first plan is to remove any error and/or problem present in the current released version.  I want to have program updated to support all new HTML commands (and probably also the new HTTP 1.1 protocol) which will be released in next months.  In the version 3.0 I'll implement a GUI (surely MUI).

   Anyone who want suggest new functions or other HTML commands or have bugs to report can send me an email.

@EndNode

